														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2321440">
									

<p>I can see why it would be.</p>
<p>The idea behind the event itself was that taking fluid samples was not his reason for interacting with her. He was supposed to be performing a test of a different nature.</p>
<p>The idea behind having the event is to humanize her by making the reader sympathize for her. It opens up the opportunity for her to humanize the whole family.</p>
<p>Yes, it is jarring. There was at least some intent behind that.</p>
<p>Does that make sense? Does it not work?</p>

							</div>

								
					
