			<div class="content" id="post-content-2377993">
									

<p>For what it matters, I thought the log was well written and adds to the article. Callous indifference on the part of foundation personnel is what is being demonstrated.</p>
<p>Yes, it would be standard procedure for medical stuff performed on a woman to be done by a woman. They don't care enough to do that, though, because they are treating her like just another thing (which some ass tried to take advantage of). She got pissed and spoke out.</p>

